{"tid":1968233,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【教學】Steam食差價買game","createTime":"2020-04-11T13:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T20:07:40.000Z","uid":55471,"like":2,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4c629dd87ea5f659182d2e22295e7b475cb51aea","tid":1968233,"uid":55471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"疫情下希望呢個post可以幫到大家用平既價錢買到更加多既遊戲！！！<br />\n唔知玩開正版game既各位有冇成日比steam既遊戲定價搞到買得落手呢？我知應該有好多人都識得點樣利用呢個漏洞去買game，但我都想係度同大家分享下點樣可以食到差價。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8wp8SsK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8wp8SsK.jpg&h=53afa3cb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n大家係上面個張圖應該見到隻GREEN HELL係香港Steam係賣緊HKD$81.75，而同一個版本係第二個地區只係賣緊隻game一半價錢都冇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3QF0JBa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3QF0JBa.png&h=b901769c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n計翻匯率HKD$25左右。<br />\n咁究竟點樣轉區呢？大家只係需要幾樣野：VPN，Steam充值卡，一個有效地址。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2cid3DD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2cid3DD.png&h=29399e4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先，大家先要一個用到既VPN，小弟我平時用睇開netflix都會用到VPN，咁我個人就用緊ExpressVPN，大家係電腦裝完之後只需要將VPN轉去阿根廷。但係<span style=\"color: red;\">記住</span>一定要事先登出左你個steam AC先！！！<br />\n連接左VPN之後，大家可以登入翻steam，呢個時候我地就入去帳戶詳細資料呢一版。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TuFczMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTuFczMA.jpg&h=f12bee92&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n大家會見到自己地區仲係寫住香港，但無需要擔心，因為呢一刻你已經可以更新商店國家地區。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AaUg1s7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAaUg1s7.png&h=3bd04b4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係呢度大家可以選擇阿根廷，之後應該會叫你寫地址，姓名。咁小弟我係呢度就填左我地偉大既祖國駐阿根廷領使館作為地址，姓名填乜都得。跟住你應該就成功轉左你既商店地區去阿根廷。<br />\n下面繼續"},{"pid":"6a75cf2cffe13148e83b135493d388f78131a003","tid":1968233,"uid":2734,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T13:41:16.000Z","msg":"呢D野自己私下做啦 仲咁大聲 幾多人俾人鎖ACC"},{"pid":"81324e44038e781d8462e901812e9e35b5c1fbfe","tid":1968233,"uid":24857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T13:42:09.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b9ad1ad06de41fd7b5ed9cd0161c5a4bc537fef2","tid":1968233,"uid":55471,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T13:43:13.000Z","msg":"大家係呢個時候就可以將你既steam登出，之後關閉VPN。理論上你個steam地區已經係轉左去阿根廷，個VPN用處已經係冇用。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jO5Dvo1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjO5Dvo1.jpg&h=4a5866c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89046e4c9ff865ce6ac170ad7570ccceecf535f6","tid":1968233,"uid":50660,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T13:45:28.000Z","msg":"果小小錢搞咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f996c0896698e36a1ce28f96c220c97785bfbf4f","tid":1968233,"uid":30927,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T13:46:56.000Z","msg":"教人開vpn買game, ban左你比返acc人? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e837f20f96e144392e7312677f50ac75eceb6fd1","tid":1968233,"uid":6530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T13:48:51.000Z","msg":"交你老母稅fun son<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90bf133f6b01f69d688cc72bf38af5603e7d2a62","tid":1968233,"uid":106027,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T13:49:40.000Z","msg":"其實得架 畀人ban果時出示返當日機票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5345af09fb62ea657278ac21bb7b3d886ba5818","tid":1968233,"uid":55471,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T13:49:59.000Z","msg":"上面錯手send左出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZmUs8bu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZmUs8bu.jpg&h=c744f20a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新增資金至STEAM 錢包呢一part大家係一定要用禮物卡，因為steam已經封鎖左要使用當地信用卡，禮物卡係邊買大家自己搵啦。<br />\n去到呢一步大家已經完成，入左錢，就可以買得game玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 以上係個人分享only，會有比steam封既風險，而且某d game計翻匯率係會貴過香港steam，呢d大多數都唔係steam獨家遊戲，買之前記住計下匯率。"},{"pid":"7967ec5f6100af24a448c9bfe3d4584eb609ec46","tid":1968233,"uid":20890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T13:52:18.000Z","msg":"大把人識啦<br />\n問題我唔會貪果幾十蚊做到肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00fc4bbf6cdbd2bf5d5e002f774de70ce812758f","tid":1968233,"uid":55471,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f996c0896698e36a1ce28f96c220c97785bfbf4f","tid":1968233,"uid":30927,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T13:46:56.000Z","msg":"教人開vpn買game, ban左你比返acc人? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T13:52:21.000Z","msg":"所以我咪講明有風險咯"},{"pid":"7ba32464601a7bb960f9ccedc10779f94ed86eac","tid":1968233,"uid":114964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T13:57:57.000Z","msg":"乞衣"},{"pid":"92a80c30d54a391a4ce82f7c2bbe7ad909d14fad","tid":1968233,"uid":311004,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:00:58.000Z","msg":"好易比人ban成個帳<br />\n仲不如直接去買零售網啲key <br />\n頂多收回遊戲"},{"pid":"158518c5957cb775befb4cf45fcdb3b99d7ada41","tid":1968233,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:02:40.000Z","msg":"又黎?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9992553f0f7044eaa0d76a5249af5becfeae67b","tid":1968233,"uid":55471,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"92a80c30d54a391a4ce82f7c2bbe7ad909d14fad","tid":1968233,"uid":311004,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:00:58.000Z","msg":"好易比人ban成個帳<br />\n仲不如直接去買零售網啲key <br />\n頂多收回遊戲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:04:13